<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-08-25T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-08-25T00:00:00-05:00" n="888" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d888">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/13007.</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">R. Zubáran
                                    Capmany</persName> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                                    State</gloss>.</hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Confidential Agency of the
                                        Constitutionalist Government of Mexico</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-08-25">
                                    <hi rend="italic">August 25, 1914</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>The undersigned, Confidential Agent of the Chief of the Constitutional
                            Army of Mexico, Don Venustiano Carranza, in compliance with special
                            instructions, has the honor of informing the Government of the United
                            States, through the very dign conduct of the Honorable Secretary of
                            State, that on the twenty-second day of August of this year, Mr.
                            Carranza took charge of the Executive Power of the Mexican Republic in
                            accordance with the Plan of Guadalupe of March twenty-six, nineteen
                            hundred and thirteen.</p>
                        <p>The undersigned avails himself [etc.]</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">R. Zubáran Capmany</hi></signed>.</closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>